{
  "texts": [
    "One way to leverage LLMs for this task is through fewshot learning, by providing some labeled examples of past user stories and their estimated points to improve the model's ability to estimate new stories.",
    "However, the choice and number of examples can impact the estimation effectiveness.",
    "Tawosi et al.",
    "propose Search-Based Optimisation for StoryPoint Estimation (SBSE) to optimize the example selection through a multi-objective approach [122].",
    "They use NSGA-II to simultaneously optimize three objective functions -the sum of absolute errors, the confidence interval of the error distribution, and the number of examples."
  ]
}